The Forge
Category Zone

Occupants

The Forge is a location in the Dwarven Mines located next to the Forge Basin. Its functionality can be used after reaching Heart of the Mountain Tier 2.

Discovery Text

The following text is displayed when you enter the The Forge for the first time:

NEW AREA DISCOVERED!
⏣ The Forge

■ Refine ores and cast items at the Forge!

Purpose

The Forge allows players to create various items, including Tools, Weapons, Armor, Pets, Accessories and more. The Forge menu can be accessed by speaking to a Forger or by calling Fred with an Abiphone, after reaching Heart of the Mountain Tier 2.

Players start out with 2 forge slots, but can earn 5 more by unlocking Heart of the Mountain Tier 3-7, for a total of 7 slots.

Click to view!

Forge Recipes are separated into nine sections, and they can also be searched for in game using the Search button in the Forge Recipes menu. Each item recipe requires specific ingredients and has a set duration for how long it takes to forge. Forge slots that are forging an item can not be used until the item is finished and taken out.

Forge Time Upgrades

There are two ways to reduce the amount of time an item takes to forge (both additive):

Source Amount
Heart of the Mountain Quick Forge perk 10% + 0.5% per level, 30% at level 20
Cole's Molten Forge perk 25%

Having Quick Forge 20 and Cole's Molten Forge perk active results in a total 55% time reduction.

Additionally, the Gemstone Gauntlet's Kinetic ability reduces your ongoing Forge timers by 0.5s for each Perfect Gemstone it has when you kill a Mob on a Mining Island, for a max of 2.5s per kill.

History

SkyBlock Prototype
January 15th, 2021 Dwarven Mines Release The Forge Added.
January 20th, 2021 Minor Patch Added +1 Forge Slot for Heart of the Mountain tiers 3 and 4.
March 30th, 2021 0.11.3 Made the Forge notification clickable to warp to the Forge.
July 20th, 2021 Minor Patch Item data is now passed to new items in the Forge, such as Drills.
November 8th, 2021 Minor Patch The Forge menu now uses the Talisman Of Coins texture to represent Coins instead of Golden Nuggets.
April 21st, 2022 Minor Patch Warping to the Forge now makes you face south.
August 6th, 2024 Artist's Abode Fixed a typo in forge error message.
September 17th, 2024 0.20.6 Added 2 new Forge slots, for a total of 7.
Added Search and Forge Recipes buttons.
Replaced the Refine Ores and Item Casting categories and with 9 new, more specific categories.
Removed the Mithril Pickaxe and Refined Mithril Pickaxe from the Forge and into Bubu's shop.
All Drills now take 30s to forge, except the first in their line.
All Drill Engines and Fuel Tanks now only take 30s to forge, except the first in their line.
All Chisels now only take 30s to forge, except the first one.
All Reforge Stones now only take 6h to forge.
All Upgrade Modules now only take 18h to forge.
Increased the forge time of Armor Of Divan from 23 -> 24 hours per piece.
